Package psidev.psi.mi.jami.model

Interface Alias

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultAlias, MitabAlias, XmlAlias, XmlAlias, XmlAlias
    public interface Alias
    Alias is a synonym. It is composed of a name and a type. Ex: alias type = 'gene' and name = 'BRCA2'
    Since:
    22/11/12
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Marine Dumousseau (marine@ebi.ac.uk)

    • Method Detail

      • getType

        CvTerm getType()
        The alias type is a controlled vocabulary term. The type can be null. Ex : gene name, gene synonym, locus name, ...
        Returns:
        the type of the current alias

      • getName

        String getName()
        Alias name cannot be null. Ex: TP53, BRCA2, ..
        Returns:
        the alias name.
